content:
Hi, I don't see a tag for "already voted," just voting by mail or in person. Should I select mail and just skip sending the info text?
Campaign: VBM_102524_PA_ET_type: dvc
This script does not have an already voted option.  Select who they plan to vote for and how.
So if they already voted, do I mark that as mail?
For PA yes as they don't have in person early voting.  Some states are going to have more options.
